issue.title: Migrate rpc-tests.sh to rpc-tests.py
issue.body:
These are cherry-picks to switch to rpc-tests.py

I have cherry-picked up to the point where Core swiched to python3. So this is all python2.

Commits are cherry-picked from several PRs. 
I find the most notable to be:
* https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/6616
* https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/6804
* https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/7135
